  ('judicial-cf446b4c-moex-00138', 'judicial-cf446b4c', 'judicial-cf446b4c-moex-113-f335c5ad', 'sub-judicial-cf446b4c-02', NULL, 'essay', '債權人甲以對債務人乙新臺幣（下同）600 萬元借款債權所取得之勝訴
